Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_daintmsk

Device All Endpoints Interrupt Mask Register (DAINTMSK)

The Device Endpoint Interrupt Mask register works with the Device Endpoint Interrupt register to interrupt the application when an event occurs on a device endpoint. However, the Device All Endpoints Interrupt (DAINT) register bit corresponding to that interrupt will still be set. Mask Interrupt: 1'b0 Unmask Interrupt: 1'b1
